namePublishedin: Sitzungsber. Math.-Phys. Cl. Königl. Bayer. Akad. Wiss. München 8: 264. 1878 [1 Jun 1878]

nomenclaturalStatus: orth. var.    Miquel (pp. 87-88) used the name ‘Paullinia diversiflora’ and referenced to DC. (Prodr. 1: 304, 306. 1824; Ann. Mus. Natl. Hist. Nat. 4: 350 (‘349’). 1804).  However, DC. used P. diversifolia Jacq., and Miquel’s usage of ‘P. diversiflora’ is treated as a typographical error
